  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0baf \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd ; 13 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1 ; 20 \u0bae\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Attack on Velwaya filling station; 13 people arrested; Rescue of 20 motorcycles",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "13 people have been arrested for attacking a petrol filling station in Wellawaya area. Wellawaya police said that the suspects were arrested yesterday.",
        "An attack has been carried out on a fuel station in the Wellawaya area under the Wellawaya police division",
        "There was a tense situation as the general public waiting in line at the filling station was informed that the supply of fuel for distribution was over.",
        "Following this, it is reported that the public attacked the fuel station by throwing stones and bottles.",
        "A police officer was injured and a fuel station was also damaged.",
        "So far 13 people have been arrested in connection with the incident and 20 motorcycles have been seized by the police.",
        "The arrested suspects are between the ages of 18 and 45 and belong to Bassara, Ethiliveya and Wellawaya areas."
      ],
